---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "@components/CTAButton.astro";
import { BRAND } from "~/lib/brand";
---
<BaseLayout seo={{ title: "About Northvale Roofing", description: "Founder story, crew philosophy, and why we're different from every other roofer in the Yellow Pages.", pathname: "/about" }}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">We built Northvale because we were tired of how roofing usually goes.</h1>
    <article class="prose-northvale mt-8">
      <p>Most roofing sales look the same: a stranger in a truck, a verbal number, a pressure close before the neighbor next door signs with someone else. The homeowner ends up either overpaying for what they got, or underpaying for something that fails in year seven.</p>
      <p>We built {BRAND.name} to do it the way we'd want it done to our own houses. <strong>Same-day inspection. Written estimate before we leave the driveway. A named project manager on every job.</strong> No dispatcher, no "one of our team members will reach out."</p>
      <h2>What you get</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>A 10+ year foreman on every crew — not a first-week helper running a nail gun.</li>
        <li>A forty-photo documentation packet at job close. It's yours; we also send a copy to your insurance file.</li>
        <li>GAF Timberline HDZ as the default — a 50-year non-prorated warranty when installed to spec, which we do.</li>
        <li>No subcontracting the foreman role. Crews are our people.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>What we won't do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We don't knock doors after a storm. That's a Texas Bus. & Com. Code § 27.02 minefield, and more importantly, it's how neighbors get burned.</li>
        <li>We don't waive deductibles. It's insurance fraud — not a gray area.</li>
        <li>We don't bid against $7K full-replacement numbers. If that's the price you need, we're not your roofer. We'll happily tell you what's missing in that bid.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <div class="mt-10 flex gap-3">
      <CTAButton href="/contact" label="Book my inspection" ctaId="about-book" />
      <CTAButton href="/reviews" variant="ghost" label="Read reviews" />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
